ğŸ—ï¸ Build & Run

Local Dev

npm install
npm run dev

App runs at http://localhost:5173.

Build

npm run build
npm run preview


â¸»

ğŸŒ Deployment

Vercel

Add this vercel.json:

{
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [{ "src": "dist/**", "use": "@vercel/static" }],
  "routes": [{ "src": "/(.*)", "dest": "/index.html" }]
}

Render (Static)

Add render.yaml:

services:
  - type: web
    name: fb-group-poster
    env: static
    buildCommand: npm ci && npm run build
    staticPublishPath: dist


